<TEXT>&#2;<DATELINE>2020</DATELINE><TITLE>Biosafety Consensus for 2019 Novel Coronavirus Pneumonia in Clinical Laboratory</TITLE><BODY>With the outbreak and spread of the 2019 Novel Coronavirus pneumonia, laboratory biosafety has become increasingly prominent. The Society of Laboratory Medicine of Chinese Medical Association formulates this guideline with reference to Chinese National Recommendations and relevant documents. From the perspectives of Microbiology, Epidemiology, Case Definition, Safety Principles, Personal Precaution, Specimen Collection, Specimen Transport, Specimen Handling, Analysis, Post-Analysis and Emergencies, this guideline gives recommendations on biosafety precaution and biosafety protection. We hope that it can be practically implemented and continuously improved to ensure laboratory safety.&#3;</BODY></TEXT>